        <tr>
            <td><hr /></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <span id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl1_Label1"><p>Iperius Backup is very easy to install and try out. There is only one and small-size installation file for all editions. The version that is installed by default is the Freeware one, that can be immediately converted in the Trial version (21 days) or activated using a purchased license code. In order to try Iperius [&hellip;]</p>
